For edkrepo.bat and edkrepo_dev.py use, this folder has the highest priority to be selected as the edkrepo global data directory.  
If EDK2_EDKREPO_PATH is not set, or this directory does not exist, the default C:/ProgramData/edkrepo/ directory will be used. 

User must add an edkrepo.cfg file to this folder before use.
User may add edkrepo_user.cfg file to this folder.

